FORMAT: 1A
HOST: https://furniture-store-api.mockapiary.com

# Furniture Store API

A RESTful API for managing furniture products and customer orders.
Admins manage furniture. Clients can browse and order without signing in.

---

## Furniture Collection [/furniture]

### Get All Furniture (Public) [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    [
        {
            "id": 1,
            "name": "Wooden Chair",
            "description": "Strong wooden chair",
            "price": 1500,
            "imageUrl": "https://example.com/chair.jpg"
        }
    ]

---

### Create Furniture (Admin) [POST]

+ Request (application/json)
    {
        "name": "Modern Sofa",
        "description": "Comfortable 3-seat sofa",
        "price": 5000,
        "imageUrl": "https://example.com/sofa.jpg"
    }

+ Response 201 (application/json)
    {
        "id": 2,
        "name": "Modern Sofa",
        "description": "Comfortable 3-seat sofa",
        "price": 5000,
        "imageUrl": "https://example.com/sofa.jpg"
    }

---

## Single Furniture [/furniture/{id}]

+ Parameters
    + id: 1 (number) - Furniture ID

### Get Furniture by ID (Public) [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    {
        "id": 1,
        "name": "Wooden Chair",
        "description": "Strong wooden chair",
        "price": 1500,
        "imageUrl": "https://example.com/chair.jpg"
    }

---

### Update Furniture (Admin) [PUT]

+ Request (application/json)
    {
        "name": "Updated Chair",
        "price": 1700
    }

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    {
        "id": 1,
        "name": "Updated Chair",
        "price": 1700
    }

---

### Delete Furniture (Admin) [DELETE]

+ Response 204


## Order Collection [/orders]

### Place an Order (Client) [POST]

+ Request (application/json)
    {
        "furnitureId": 1,
        "customerName": "Feven Tolosa",
        "phoneNumber": "+251912345678"
    }

+ Response 201 (application/json)
    {
        "orderId": 101,
        "message": "Order placed successfully"
    }
